Class ObjArray<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.util.ObjArray<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadOnlyObjList<E>, Cloneable, Iterable<E>

    public final class ObjArray<E>
extends Object
implements ReadOnlyObjList<E>, Iterable<E>, Cloneable
    Wrapper for arrays of objects which provides proper equals() and hashCode() methods, and behaves nicely with Java 1.5 generics.
